They joined Crazysane Records to release their debut LP, Hunki Bobo, in May ‚Äô24, which was met with wide critical acclaim. Since then, they‚Äôve toured Europe and released another impressive album, Three Sisters, in June ‚Äô25, introducing Francis‚Äô sweet vocals to the mix. Drawing influence from bands such as The Meters, W.I.T.C.H., CAN, and Kikagaku Moyo, these melomaniacs concoct a sonic purity that resists being nailed down.
